{
  "stem": "18637.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They used to send us whatever, parcels.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there came papers to go to Los Angeles, to my aunt and uncle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But from the union here, from Toronto, it came a delegation that would take some tailors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my husband worked before the war as a tailor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They really did-- they really wanted to take out some-- some people from there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we came here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- right after the war, in Bindermichl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived on the same block.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I lived upstairs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he lived downstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We usually, even then, you-- you lived in the same.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was blocks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody had a room or two rooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it probably wasn't easy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the-- the fear goes with you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it's easier to go from slavery to freedom than from freedom to slavery.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are adjustable things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, if-- if I would say 100% no, I-- I-- it wouldn't be true.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It affected.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- but your mind, you can change things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It has to be this way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You look forward.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know what somebody said in the-- that when a-- a little leaf falls, you're sorry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when the whole-- when the whole tree falls, then you get-- you have in common with some other people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they're all in the same boat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I consider myself lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had a sister and my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My husband had three brothers and a sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the millions of people, they just-- thousands of people, they just survived, just by themselves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So in a way, I was lucky, luckier than other people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE] officers killed my three cousins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my-- my sister had-- my mother had a sister, five girls and a son-- nobody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Pinsk, my brother-- my-- my father had a sister, with four sons and two daughters.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
